Depictions of a fictional [[theocracy|theocratic]] societies recur in [[science fiction]], [[speculative fiction]] and [[fantasy]]. Such depictions are mostly [[dystopian]], and in some cases humorous or satirical; positively presented theocracies are very much the exception.
Some fictional theocracies are based on a future or [[alternate history]] development of actual [[religion]]s, whilst in others the religions depicted are wholly fictional.
The following table is sorted by time of publication (for series, time of earliest publication).
