{| class="wikitable" |- ! style="text-align:center;" colspan="6"|'''Zoroastrianism honorifics and titles''' |- ! scope="col" style="width:300px;"| Role ! scope="col" style="width:600px;"| Description |- | [[Mobad]], Mobedyar | |- | [[Herbad]] | |- | [[Dastur]] | |}
== Various == === Magicians ===
There are many kinds of people who deal with [[magic (paranormal)|magic]]. They include [[Magician (paranormal)|paranormal magicians]], [[Magician (fantasy)|fantasy magicians]], [[shaman]]s, [[kalku]], and the [[magi]]. In [[Shamanic magic]], the [[Seid (shamanic magic)|Seid]] plays a role, as does the [[Warlock]] and [[Witch]] in Paganism. In history, [[magic in the Greco-Roman world]] was common. There are also the [[Onmyōdō|Onmyou Mystic]] and the [[Bomoh]].
