In Christian theology, a '''supernatural gift''' is a gift of God that is conferred on man that is above all the powers of created nature.<reF>{{CathEncy|wstitle=Supernatural Gift}}</ref> An example of this is the gift of [[Grace (Christianity)|grace]] which enables man to attain salvation despite [[original sin]].

